pageProduct.name: Swisse Ultiboost Bilberry 30 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Bilberry is a premium quality formula to help support eye health and provide antioxidant support.

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Bilberry is a premium quality formula to help support eye health and provide antioxidant support.

Eye Health: The eyes are susceptible to oxidative stress. The antioxidants in Bilberry may help support and protect eye health.

Antioxidant: Bilberry is a source of antioxidants. Antioxidants help protect cells against free radical damage.

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Bilberry has been formulated based on scientific evidence to support eye health in a convenient, one-a-

day dose.

Lifestyle Claim: Vegetarian

Size: 30 Tablets

Ingredients

Contains: EACH TABLET CONTAINS: BILBERRY (Vaccinium myrtillus) extract equiv. to fresh fruit 15g (equiv. to anthocyanosides 60mg)

Allergen Free From: Artificial Flavours| Egg| Gluten| Lactose| Soy| Yeast

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
One tablet daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C. Do not use if cap seal is broken.

Storage Temperature: Store below 25°C
